Actress Mercy Johnson Okojie has stated her first daughter, Purity is smitten with love for Wizkid’s first baby mama, Shola Ogudu. Purity, who attends the same school as Wizkid’s son, Tife, also travelled to Dubai in the company of her father for the sports competition where she represented her school in swimming at the World School Games. The mother of four made this known in an Instagram post where she expressed immense pride for her daughter’s accomplishment while thanking Shola for cheering her daughter in her absence. She also expressed gratitude to the mother of one for sharing photos and videos with captured precious moments from the games with her.   Will Smith is best actor at BAFTA 2022     ‘Portable needs rehab not shows’     Nigerian comedians can sell out 02 arena – Kenny Blaq   In another post, the film star, sharing photos of her daughter with her father and others with Wizkid’s son, informed her daughter has been drooling over her. “The ojoro that happens in this house ehh @princeodiokojie and Purity in Dubai….I can’t believe she picked her dad over me. Infact Henry and I are making our trip next…..plus she keeps saying bolu’s mum is so cool @o.oluwanishola,” she wrote. Reacting to the post, Shola wrote: “Look at my babies!!!!!!! Purity is my new bestie o, I’ll come carry her from you sooon.” In turn, Mercy Johnson commenting under Shola’s wrote: @o.oluwanishola sis come carry oo. she is med about you and it’s an awesome thing.”